::Prowl::

A face slowly comes into focus, the face of a beautiful femm. For a second, 
Prowl didn't know who the face belonged to, or where he was, but it 
eventually came flooding back to him.

He was in the Cybertronian Fire, the ship serving as the Maximal base. He had 
been severely injured in a battle somewhere... Yes, that must have been the 
reason he felt like his limbs was about to fall off. His optics come fully 
online, or as fully as his damage can let them, and he finally recognizes the 
face.

It was Iron Raptor's, the love of his life. For a second, Prowl wondered why 
she seemed to be crying, but then realized that it was probably about him.

"Am... Am I alive?" he says, trying to sit up but wincing with pain as his 
torso acomplishes nothing but a slight jerk.
